Class JsonConcurrentMap

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractMap<String,Object>
java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentHashMap<String,Object>
com.webfirmframework.wffweb.json.JsonConcurrentMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonBaseNode, JsonMapNode, JsonPart, Serializable, ConcurrentMap<String,Object>, Map<String,Object>
public non-sealed class JsonConcurrentMap extends ConcurrentHashMap<String,Object> implements JsonMapNode, Serializable
To parse json object string: 

 JsonMapNode jsonMap = JsonConcurrentMap.parse("""
             {
             "key" : "value",
             "key1" : "value1"
             }
             """);
 // To get value
 String key1Value = jsonMap.getValueAsString("key1");

 // Prints value
 System.out.println("key1Value = " + key1Value); // key1Value = value1

 String jsonString = jsonMap.toJsonString();
 // Prints json string
 System.out.println("jsonString = " + jsonString); // jsonString = {"key1":"value1","key":"value"}
Since:
12.0.4
